================================================================================
 Nested vSphere Lab - Jumpbox (Stage 1)   {{ jumpbox.hostname }}.{{ jumpbox.domain }}
 Generated: {{ ansible_date_time.iso8601 }}
================================================================================

ROLE OF THIS HOST
  Router / NAT gateway, DNS, DHCP, and OCI registry for the nested vSphere lab.
  Egress is ONLY via the public NIC: {{ jumpbox.public_nic }}
  Private fabric NIC (trunk): {{ jumpbox.private_nic }} (MTU {{ mtu.private }})

VLANS / SUBNETS  (gateway = .1, owned by this jumpbox)
{% for v in vlans_computed %}
  - VLAN {{ v.id }} {{ '(native)' if v.is_native else '        ' }} {{ v.name }}
      subnet : {{ v.cidr }}
      gateway: {{ v.gateway }}   iface: {{ v.iface }}
      DHCP   : {{ 'enabled  ' + v.dhcp_start + ' - ' + v.dhcp_end if v.dhcp else 'disabled' }}
{% endfor %}

DNS  ({{ vlans_computed | selectattr('is_native') | map(attribute='gateway') | first }})
  forward zone : {{ jumpbox.domain }}
  forwarders   : {{ dns.forwarders | join(', ') }}
  pre-created records:
{% for r in dns.records | default([]) %}
    {{ '%-20s' | format(r.name + '.' + jumpbox.domain) }} {{ r.ip }}
{% endfor %}

TIME (NTP)
  No local NTP server. Nested nodes use upstream via NAT (DHCP option 42):
    {{ ntp.upstream | join(', ') }}

OCI REGISTRY (Harbor)
  URL      : https://{{ registry.fqdn }}/
  IP       : {{ harbor_ip }}
  data dir : {{ registry.data_dir }}
  admin    : admin  (password: stored in your ansible-vault secrets.yml)
{% if (registry.proxy_cache | default([])) | length > 0 %}
  proxy-cache projects: {{ registry.proxy_cache | map(attribute='name') | join(', ') }}
{% endif %}

PKI / CA  (trusted end-to-end; distributed to nested nodes in Stage 2)
  mode        : {{ certs.ca_mode }}
  CA bundle   : {{ certs.dir }}/ca-bundle.crt
  CA key      : {{ certs.dir }}/root-ca.key  (mode 0600)
  CA backup   : {{ certs.backup_path }}/
  fingerprint : {{ ca_fingerprint | default('(run the certs role to compute)') }}

ARTIFACTS (OVA/ISO for Stage 2)
  local folder: {{ artifacts.dir }}

NEXT STEP
  Stage 2 will deploy nested ESXi + vCenter and enable Supervisor, reusing this
  jumpbox's DNS, DHCP, CA bundle, and Harbor registry.
================================================================================
